=head1 DESCRIPTION

The automatically created recovery point of a namespace. Recovery
points are created every 30 minutes and kept for 24 hours.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 NamespaceArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the namespace the recovery point is
associated with.


=head2 NamespaceName => Str

The name of the namespace the recovery point is associated with.


=head2 RecoveryPointCreateTime => Str

The time the recovery point is created.


=head2 RecoveryPointId => Str

The unique identifier of the recovery point.


=head2 TotalSizeInMegaBytes => Num

The total size of the data in the recovery point in megabytes.


=head2 WorkgroupName => Str

The name of the workgroup the recovery point is associated with.



